 Career History



Professional

                                    Current                


Carlyle-Commscope Holdings LP






Fund Advisor

                                    Tenure Unconfirmed                


The Carlyle Group LP (Real Assets)


                  The Carlyle Group LP (Real Assets) focuses on real estate, infrastructure, energy and natural resources. Real estate funds pursue real estate investment opportunities in Asia, Europe & the United States and typically acquire single-property assets. Real estate funds invest in office buildings, hotels, retail & residential properties, industrial properties and senior living facilities. Energy and natural resources activities focus on buyouts, growth capital investments and strategic joint ventures in the midstream, upstream, power and oilfield services, and renewable energy sectors globally.                




Fund Advisor

                                    Prior                


The Carlyle Group LP (Global Market Strategies)


                  The Carlyle Group is a global, multi-product, markets-focused investment platform seeks investment opportunities in the US. Global Market Strategies manages three groups of funds Structured Credit, Hedge Funds and Carry & Financing Funds. Structured credit funds invest primarily in performing senior secured bank loans through structured vehicles and other investment products. Hedge fund strategies focus on long/short credit, commodities trading, emerging market equities and macroeconomic strategies. Carry & financing funds specialize in three strategies middle-market finance, energy mezzanine and global distressed and corporate opportunities.                





 Boards & Committees



Non-Profit Boards ▾




Member, Board of Trustees

                    Prior - 2015                  


Legal Aid Society of the District of Columbia

                    The Legal Aid Society of the District of Columbia was formed to "provide legal aid and counsel to indigent persons in civil law matters and to encourage measures by which the law may better protect and serve their needs."  The Legal Aid Society works to ensure that all of the District's residents have equal and meaningful access to justice.                  





